HostMada is proud to announce the availability and launch of the new Asia location in **Hong Kong** for all VPS services.

Our OpenVZ VPS lines are all available in Hong Kong in addition to Wilkes-Barre, Atlanta, Dallas, Los Angeles, Chicago (USA), Westland (EU) and Singapore.

The network includes premium low latency access to **China Telecom** and **China Unicom** backbone, the HKIX for local traffic and NTT GIN for Asia and international routes. By providing direct access connectivity our chinese customers get the fastest route to mainland China as well as to the huge Chinese market itself.

To celebrate our newest location, we have a _15% recurring discount_ available on all VPS at our Hong Kong data center for all new services, new clients and current clients! Just enter promotional code **HK15OFF** to receive _15% off_ every month.

